                            <head>No. 1175<lb/><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                            <p>At the 147th meeting of the National Security Council on June 1,
                                Secretary <persName corresp="#p_DJF2">Dulles</persName> discussed
                                the situation in the Near East and South Asia, including Egypt. For
                                text of the memorandum of discussion at the meeting, see <ref target="frus1952-54v09p1#d137">Document 137</ref>.</p>
